Description: Vietnamese Input Method Engine for IBus using Unikey Engine IBus is an Intelligent Input Bus. It is a new input framework for Linux OS. It provides full featured and user friendly input method user interface. It also may help developers to develop input method easily. . Ibus-Unikey is a Vietnamese input method for IBus. It uses the Unikey engine to process keyevents.
